name: Kina
description: I’m a very loving, honest, kind and loyal, seeking love, passionate, tender and caring lady. I like to dance, because I am joyful, sociable and full of energy. I’m intelligent and independent woman. I want to live for my partner and to devote every day for making our family really happy, to fill life of my close people with gentleness, love, warmth and harmony of home hearth. I do not like aggression that is why I always try to find a compromise. I am sure that it is always possible to find a way out of any situation.
